{"tid":329990,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"代問：奇蟲1問 （慎入）","createTime":"2017-07-20T20:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T14:26:55.000Z","uid":65616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c16298b679b44d324ede41852a266aff9d6487aa","tid":329990,"uid":65616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T20:33:15.000Z","msg":"最近我有個朋友屋企發現左 以下呢種昆蟲，外形似 螞蟻，但又不多似螞蟻會成群結隊咁搵野食<br />\n有沒有巴打 或 絲打知係咩品種？有殺傷力（有毒）？<br />\n我朋友話 它們不怕水，識游水，不似螞蟻遇水好快就 瓜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/043134_193388f5851189fcd6e7bd869f8f05e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F043134_193388f5851189fcd6e7bd869f8f05e0.jpg&h=bac2b2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/043134_66e33d2845e80f587dbf792e40e97cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F043134_66e33d2845e80f587dbf792e40e97cd4.jpg&h=5f102127&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14a99138a0b8d3a8f8cd6127e2771bcb441b1f44","tid":329990,"uid":88394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"捲葉象鼻蟲 (長頸象) ?<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nature.edu.hk/species_database/species/attelabidae\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.edu.hk%2Fspecies_database%2Fspecies%2Fattelabidae&d=dexsi9N9yaZrY9yHU43kTC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7ed0c0c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nature.edu.hk/species_database/species/attelabidae</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://gaga.biodiv.tw/9701bx/in94.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaga.biodiv.tw%2F9701bx%2Fin94.htm&d=dexsi9N9yaZrY9yHU43kTC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=825e225f\" target=\"_blank\">http://gaga.biodiv.tw/9701bx/in94.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a832aa368bb9453b10b3e1eaccbb36071879e3a3","tid":329990,"uid":65616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捲葉象鼻蟲 (長頸象) ?<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nature.edu.hk/species_database/species/attelabidae\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.edu.hk%2Fspecies_database%2Fspecies%2Fattelabidae&d=dexsi9N9yaZrY9yHU43kTC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7ed0c0c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nature.edu.hk/species_database/species/attelabidae</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://gaga.biodiv.tw/9701bx/in94.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaga.biodiv.tw%2F9701bx%2Fin94.htm&d=dexsi9N9yaZrY9yHU43kTC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=825e225f\" target=\"_blank\">http://gaga.biodiv.tw/9701bx/in94.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔多似，呢隻蟲 有3節，中間果節偏紅，另外果2節都係黑色<br />\n在我個fd 屋企到繁殖得好似幾快...<br />\n而且它們唔似螞蟻有固定巢穴（我個fd 話）"},{"pid":"fbf2c08c95e08bc730d48b7b16ca7f22bf2f8297","tid":329990,"uid":65616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"有沒有 巴打或絲打 屋企曾經見過它們 🙈🙈🙈"},{"pid":"7699e5a3f1918603efa0c1c08b91f061ac76d51c","tid":329990,"uid":12947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:26:55.000Z","msg":"R.I.P.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}